snippet.title: How Do You Know Mr Blue? Trailer 2018
snippet.description:
Detective Adventure game "How Do You Know Mr. Blue?" is the latest game from Swedish Indie company Winteractive.

Take the role of a private investigator following the disappearance of Mr. Blue and dive into the secrets surrounding the mysterious megacorporation C-Corp.
